                "text": "10 feet. An attic whisperer enshrouds itself in a tapestry of stolen voices. Each living creature that enters or starts their turn in the aura must succeed at a DC 19 Will save or the unnerving, bitter sobs render them distraught and they become <a aonid=\"37\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">stupefied 1</a> for as long as they remain within the aura. A creature that succeeds is temporarily immune for 1 hour. The attic whisperer can activate or deactivate the aura with a single free action, which has the <a aonid=\"32\" game-obj=\"Traits\">concentrate</a> trait."
